Hi 
This is my first simple Python project where I learned how to take input from users and show it back on the screen.

## 🧾 What this project does

This program asks the user to enter:

- Name  
- Age  
- Height (in meters)  
- Favourite number  

Then it:
- Shows data types
- Shows memory address using `id()`
- Calculates approximate birth year
- Prints a goodbye message 

## ▶️ How to run

```bash
python main.py
